title: 176. #75HARD vs Will Grumke
itunes:title: 176. #75HARD vs Will Grumke
description: Are you listening to your boss voice or your bitch voice? In today's episode, Andy is joined by Will Grumke from in-house 1st Phorm HQ. They discuss how to expose your confidence through discipline, how we must conquer the conversations we have internally, and why someone with already good habits must continue to improve.
